Author: unicornyogamat
Text: Oh yes. Every time I purge I am afraid it will be the last time. My psychiatrist has been begging me to get a physical and bloodwork for months but I can't really afford it. I worry about my heart on a daily basis. I fully expect one day to just drop dead.  I have felt like I will before. Not to get too edgy, but I kind of welcome it at this point. Take care, please. <3
